title: Wahu Aqua Disc - Surfer Blue | 100 Percent Waterproof Flying Disc Toy | Easy Throw and Catch | Ideal Garden or Beach Toy | Ages 5 Plus
features: WATERPROOF FLYING DISC TOY: Makes it easy to engage in friendly (or competitive) games of catch with friends and family for endless hours of outdoor fun
VERSATILE OUTDOOR FUN: Great for play in and out of the water to elevate all your outdoor adventures, whether you're spending time at the pool, beach, lake, park, or in your backyard
HIGH-PERFORMANCE DESIGN: Sturdy outer rim provides the perfect throw with superior air lift, accuracy, and distance for high-performance play every time
100% WATERPROOF SKIN: Made with 100% waterproof, soft neoprene skin that withstands the elements for years of quality games of catch by the pool or beach

description: From the manufacturer The Wahu Aqua Disc is perfect for a game of catch at the beach, park, garden or pool! Get ready for far-flying action with the Wahu Aqua Disc! Designed with 100% waterproof neoprene skin for incredible durability, this high performance throwing disc is equally at home in the backyard, park, pool or the beach! Super easy to throw and catch, you can take it anywhere and have a blast! Includes 1 Wahu Aqua Disc with 9.5" (24.1cm) diameter. Available in Palm Tree and Surfer designs. Recommended for ages 5 and up.
